<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1079487/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1079488" n="1"/>
  <opener><salute>Illustrissimo atque Celeberrimo Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person"><abbr>Jo.</abbr> Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelottus</rs>.</salute></opener>
  <p>Quam gratissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi fuerint humanissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, doctissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que <rs key="B_991170515107705501" type="letter">lite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><sic>Tue</sic><corr>Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice></rs>, Vir Sapientissime, Pridie Kalendas Junias isth<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c
    <lb/>datis, verbis declarare non possum. Jis, uti et compluribus
    <lb/>aliis, quibus ali<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>s me cumulasti beneficiis, me Tibi, Tuis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que omnibus, et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim ingeniosissimo, suavissimoque
    <lb/>Filio Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danieli</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternum devinxisti. Responsionem,
    <lb/>quemadmodum Tu hortatus es, ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinianam</rs> <rs key="biblio_42TNNPE9" type="biblio">De<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fension<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs> post quindecim aut 20 dies edere curabo simul
    <lb/>cum illa ipsa <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Juriniana</rs> <rs key="biblio_42TNNPE9" type="biblio">Defensione</rs>, inde et ad Te, et
    <lb/>ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newton<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinum</rs> in <rs key="place_VER-englan" type="place">Angliam</rs>, et ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118639056" type="person">Fontenelli<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>,
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11931035X" type="person">Mairanum</rs>, aliosque in <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Gallia</rs> data occasione me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>Responsionis exemplaria aliquot simul cum <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii</rs>
    <lb/>Tui <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me dilectissimi <rs key="biblio_WZBB3ZSY" type="biblio">Controversiis</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti könnte sich hier auf das vermutlich gerade im Druck befindliche Werk Daniel I. B.'s beziehen: St.4 Exercitationes quaedam mathematicae, Venetiis: Apud Dominicum Lovisam, 1724 - Werke 1, pp.297-362.</note> propedi<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> prodituris
    <lb/>transmittam. Mihi plane omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mecum <rs key="B_991170515107705501" type="letter">suprame<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moratis Tuis litteris</rs> communicasti, mihi omnino, in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam satisfaciunt. Recte facis mathematicis studiis,
    <lb/>omnique litterarum <choice><sic>commercium</sic><corr>commercio</corr></choice> valedicendo tuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudinis, quam secundam per longissimam
    <lb/>annor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> seriem Tibi exopto, causa. Nihilo tamen secius
    <lb/>non orare Te non possum, ut una adhuc tantum
    <lb/>vice quambrevissima epistola mihi explanes sequent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
    <lb/>difficultatem circa vim aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen vasis
    <lb/>alicuius effluentis motum generantem. Hac enim difficul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tate mihi amota nullus amplius circa hanc rem mihi su<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pererit scrupulus. Aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> partes laterales statim ac
    <lb/>aqua per foramen erumpere incipit nonne confluunt
         <pb facs="1079489" n="2"/>
    <lb/>ubique horizontaliter, et fortasse etiam oblique <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> lateri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus vasis, nonne, inquam, simul influunt in columnam
    <lb/>aqueam foramini vasis perpendiculariter imminent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>?
    <lb/>Si igitur confluunt ejusmodi partes aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> laterales, mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tibus suis augere poterunt vim pressionis cylindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, foramini ad perpendiculum insisten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis, se<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice> pressionem columnarum obliquarum <add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que</add> <add>ac</add> ill<add>a</add>
    <lb/>columna perpendicularis ponderantium.<note type="internal"></note> Ita, in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam, augere poterunt vim pressionis aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> colum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>n<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perpendicularis ut huius pressio ita
    <lb/>aucta <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis sit pressioni dupli ponderis cy<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> foramini vasis ad perpendicu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lum insistentis. Partes aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> laterales moveri atque
    <lb/>in cylindricam column<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> perpendiculariter foramini
    <lb/>insistent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> influere, ipse quoque falsus est, quem
    <lb/>admodum colligere poteris ex iis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> olim
    <lb/>mecum communicasti, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que legere poteris in
    <lb/>mea <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Dissertatione</rs> de Separatione Fluidor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/><abbr>pag.</abbr> 128. Ibi enim, Te consentiente, scripsi: <cit><quote><hi rend="u">Deinde
      <lb/>aquam in partibus <formula>M</formula>,<formula>R</formula>, existentem revera se<add>se</add> move<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re, atque spatium <formula>SECCES</formula> influere ad perturband<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>motum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> delabentis per istam commentitiam
      <lb/>Cataractam <formula>SECCES</formula>, probat sequens experiment<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>.</hi></quote></cit>
</p>
<p>Ut super hac re quamcitissime per <rs key="place_GEO-2775220" type="place">Oenipont<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
  <lb/>fieri poterit ad me quid Tibi videatur scribas
  <lb/>pro sola hac vice etiam atque etiam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so,
  <lb/>et oro. Exhortor assidu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Ornatissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Filium
             <pb facs="1079490" n="3"/>
    <lb/>Tuum</rs>, quem loco Filii semper habebo, ut mecum
  <lb/>practicam Medicin<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> omnibus aliis studiis relictis
  <lb/>excolat. Ipse se id quamprimum facturum summa
  <lb/>cum animi attentione sancte pollicitus est mihi.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale,
  <lb/>Celeberrime, Amicissimeque Vir, Vale, inquam, plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>,
  <lb/>mihique, quod facis, favere perge.</salute>
<dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> Pridie
  <lb/>Kalendas Julias 1724.</dateline>
